dden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 13, 2022</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104siw1665702927115.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/siw1665702927115.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/siw1665702927115.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"siw1665702927115\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n       Database Connector Options\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"siw1665702927115__database_connector_options_144791\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Most Uniface database connectors have optional parameters, known as connector options. Connector options usually set database-specific parameters; some connector options are available on many database connectors.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"siw1665702927115__p_d47534e1_d47535e1_d47536e1\">Connector options are set in the [DRIVER_SETTINGS] section of the application assignment file, using the following syntax:</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"siw1665702927115__p_d47537e1_d47538e1_d47539e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">USYS$<var class=\"keyword varname\">Mnemonic</var>_PARAMS</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Option1</var> {<code class=\"ph codeph\">,</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Option2</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">,</code> ... <code class=\"ph codeph\">,</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">OptionN</var>}</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"siw1665702927115__p_d47540e1_d47541e1_d47542e1\">For more information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"msq1665702542189.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/msq1665702542189.html\" title=\"Use the [DRIVER_SETTINGS] section of the assignment file to specify the database and component engine connectors used, and their parameter options. The options available depend on the connector in use.\">[DRIVER_SETTINGS]</a>.</p>\n<div class=\"example\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"siw1665702927115__p_d47543e1_d47544e1_d47545e1\">For example.</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">[DRIVER_SETTINGS] \nORA = U6.1 \nUSYS$ORA_PARAMS = open cursors 40, dpa</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"siw1665702927115__topic_d31037e1_d31038e1_d31039e1_d31040e1_d31041e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d676307e104\">\n                  \n Common Connector Options\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"siw1665702927115__p_d47549e1_d47550e1_d47551e1\">Connector options that are common to several database connectors are listed as subtopics.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2532002\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2532002\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Database Connector Options Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 13, 2022 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Database Connector Options Most Uniface database connectors have optional parameters, known as connector options. Connector options usually set database-specific parameters; some connector options are available on many database connectors. Connector options are set in the [DRIVER_SETTINGS] section of the application assignment file, using the following syntax: USYS$ Mnemonic _PARAMS Option1 { , Option2 , ... , OptionN } For more information, see [DRIVER_SETTINGS] . For example. [DRIVER_SETTINGS] ORA = U6.1 USYS$ORA_PARAMS = open cursors 40, dpa Copy Common Connector Options Connector options that are common to several database connectors are listed as subtopics. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}